Fixed vs Sticky while scrolling
position: fixed
→ Always stays in same position
→ Does NOT move while scrolling
position: sticky
→ Acts like relative
→ When scroll reaches top value → becomes fixed



Difference: Relative vs Sticky
Relative:
 → Always moves from original position
 → Does not react to scroll
Sticky:
 → Acts normal initially
 → Sticks when scroll limit reached
 → Requires top, bottom, etc.

